---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Three founders. 34 years combined experience. No juniors. You always talk to the people who built the system."
>
  <Section class="pt-28 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="mb-6">You always talk to the people who built the system.</h1>
      <p class="text-secondary-text text-xl leading-relaxed">
        WKTW is three founders with 45 years of combined experience in digital growth,
        technical infrastructure, and content strategy &mdash; split across three
        non-overlapping registers, not three slightly different versions of the same
        r&eacute;sum&eacute;. No juniors. No account managers. The people who built
        the diagnostic tools are the people you work with.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <Section elevated>
    <h2 class="mb-4">The team</h2>
    <p class="text-secondary-text text-lg mb-10 max-w-3xl">
      Each pillar of The Get Right is owned by a founder whose career is built on it.
      Category authority, function-head operating depth, and engineering rigor &mdash;
      three credibility surfaces, zero overlap.
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div id="jon-lister" class="flex flex-col bg-bg-surface border border-border-subtle rounded-xl p-8 scroll-mt-24">
        <img
          src="/team/jon-lister.webp"
          alt="Jon Lister"
          width="112"
          height="112"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full object-cover border border-border-subtle mb-6"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-1">Jon Lister</h3>
        <p class="text-accent text-sm font-mono mb-1">Founder | Chief Executive Officer</p>
        <p class="text-secondary-text text-sm font-mono mb-3">23 Years &middot; Category Authority</p>
        <p class="text-secondary-text">
          Forbes-featured on Generative Engine Optimization. Decades of experience
          in connecting brands to their audience in ways that drive conversion.
          Public voice for one of the most impact-focused AI-search positioning
          bets in the agency world.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mt-auto pt-5 -ml-3">
          <a
            href="mailto:jon@weknowthewhy.com"
            aria-label="Email Jon Lister"
            class="p-3 text-secondary-text hover:text-accent transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jonathanlister1/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="Jon Lister on LinkedIn"
            class="p-3 text-secondary-text hover:text-accent transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M4.98 3.5A2.5 2.5 0 112.5 1a2.5 2.5 0 012.48 2.5zM.24 8.04h4.52V24H.24V8.04zm7.4 0h4.33v2.18h.06c.6-1.14 2.08-2.34 4.28-2.34 4.58 0 5.42 3.01 5.42 6.93V24h-4.52v-6.79c0-1.62-.03-3.7-2.26-3.7-2.26 0-2.6 1.76-2.6 3.58V24H7.64V8.04z" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="jason-bauman" class="flex flex-col bg-bg-surface border border-border-subtle rounded-xl p-8 scroll-mt-24">
        <img
          src="/team/jason-bauman.webp"
          alt="Jason Bauman"
          width="112"
          height="112"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full object-cover border border-border-subtle mb-6"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-1">Jason Bauman</h3>
        <p class="text-accent text-sm font-mono mb-1">Founder | Chief Product Officer</p>
        <p class="text-secondary-text text-sm font-mono mb-3">12 Years &middot; Function-head operating depth</p>
        <p class="text-secondary-text">
          Marketing technologist working the transition from ranking-based search
          to AI-mediated retrieval. A decade of technical SEO at enterprise scale
          gave him the engineering instincts and the scar tissue &mdash; pipelines
          that ship under heavy review, optimizations that must prove out. Muttr
          and Delphi are what that experience builds now.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mt-auto pt-5 -ml-3">
          <a
            href="mailto:jason@mediumroast.dev"
            aria-label="Email Jason Bauman"
