      </div>
      <div id="brandon-griner" class="flex flex-col bg-bg-surface border border-border-subtle rounded-xl p-8 scroll-mt-24">
        <img
          src="/team/brandon-griner.webp"
          alt="Brandon Griner"
          width="112"
          height="112"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full object-cover border border-border-subtle mb-6"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-1">Brandon Griner</h3>
        <p class="text-accent text-sm font-mono mb-1">Founder | Chief Technology Officer</p>
        <p class="text-secondary-text text-sm font-mono mb-3">10 Years &middot; Engineering rigor</p>
        <p class="text-secondary-text">
          Holds a BS in Computer Science and an MS in Data Science. He is not a
          marketer who learned data &mdash; he's a data engineer who happens to
          work in marketing. Brandon's engineering layer is what allows WKTW to
          do in days what larger agencies need weeks to accomplish. Canary is
          just the start.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mt-auto pt-5 -ml-3">
          <a
